
<html>
    <head>
         <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' /> 
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container lead">
            <p>Dear <%= @host.name%>,</p>
            <p>This is confirmation of a storage transaction completed between you and <%= @user.name%></p>
            <div class="card w-50">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Transaction Details</h5>
                    <table class="table">
                        <thead>
                            <th scope="col">Listing Id</th>
                            <th scope="col">User</th>
                            <th scope="col">Duration</th>
                            <th scope="col">Boxes</th>
                            <th scope="col">Price</th>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <td> <%= @transaction.listing.id %></td>
                            <td> <%= link_to @user.name,@user %></td>
                            <td> <%= @transaction.duration %></td>
                            <td> <%= @transaction.boxes %></td>
                            <td> <%= @transaction.price%></td>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>You can now remove the listing if you would like to. Please keep in touch with your renter to coordiante.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>